tionary-tt-off mw" data-term=3D"amicable" href=3D"https://www.merriam-webst=
er.com/dictionary/amicable" data-type=3D"MW">amicable</a> pair: 220 and 284=
. One can easily check that the sum of the proper divisors of 284 is 1 + 2 =
+ 4 + 71 + 142 =3D 220 and the sum of the proper divisors of 220 is 1 + 2 +=
 4 + 5 + 10 + 11 + 20 + 22 + 44 + 55 + 110 =3D 284. For those prone to numb=
